title: F.C. South End
text:
FC South End was a <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Trinidad%20and%20Tobago">Trinidad and Tobago</a> based in <a href="Point%20Fortin">Point Fortin</a>/<a href="La%20Brea%2C%20Trinidad%20and%20Tobago">La Brea</a> and is a former member of the <a href="TT%20Pro%20League">TT Pro League</a>, the highest level of football in Trinidad.
History.
Founded in 2008, it played its home games at the <a href="Manny%20Ramjohn%20Stadium">Manny Ramjohn Stadium</a>.
